{"tid":2404263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖看出香港女仔較靚,香港男人較柒","createTime":"2021-02-11T15:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T04:03:00.000Z","uid":249170,"like":8,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"609848be95ea90ae0839a8da21655c994de33629","tid":2404263,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"香港女仔全部都靚，聰明又充滿自信笑容可愛<br />\n相反香港男仔全部都好撚樣衰，眼神呆滯，好似中左輻射咁<br />\n香港男人真係輸撚哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xYqeo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xYqeo2.jpg&h=c044795c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7zXPW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7zXPW3.jpg&h=a3a5a903&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXFPF3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXFPF3b.jpg&h=5e11962f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港特有基因<br />\n生女較靚，生仔較柒較樣衰"},{"pid":"acbfd9b0143691ecdfc7b74b1d663f2c2c79e220","tid":2404263,"uid":224533,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"一個主播，兩個財佬<br />\n點比呀"},{"pid":"306270735b49ca9c7de6457316f3570dbb1aa5bf","tid":2404263,"uid":383207,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"夠薑卸妝"},{"pid":"d0213192d555b6d6d3f99399f30dec80d27c263f","tid":2404263,"uid":249170,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"306270735b49ca9c7de6457316f3570dbb1aa5bf","tid":2404263,"uid":383207,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"夠薑卸妝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"以下言論唔係我講，格離post連登護花兵講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji